graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]

    %% Required External Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|manages resources| K8s[Kubernetes 1.21+<br/>Required]

    %% Optional External Dependencies
    KubeRay -.->|webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager 1.0+<br/>Optional]
    KubeRay -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus 2.x<br/>Optional]
    KubeRay -.->|visualization| Grafana[Grafana 7.x+<br/>Optional]

    %% Ray Cluster Dependencies
    RayHead[Ray Head Pod]
    RayWorkers[Ray Worker Pods]

    KubeRay -->|creates/manages| RayHead
    KubeRay -->|creates/manages| RayWorkers

    RayHead -.->|GCS fault tolerance| Redis[External Redis 6.x+<br/>Optional]
    RayWorkers -->|connect to GCS| RayHead

    %% Optional Schedulers
    RayHead -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano 1.x<br/>Optional]
    RayHead -.->|batch scheduling| YuniKorn[YuniKorn 1.x<br/>Optional]
    RayHead -.->|job queuing| Kueue[Kueue 0.x<br/>Optional]

    %% OpenShift/RHOAI Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|creates Routes| OSRoute[OpenShift Routes<br/>RHOAI]
    KubeRay -->|uses SCC| OSSCC[OpenShift SCC<br/>RHOAI]
    KubeRay -.->|optional UI| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>RHOAI]

    %% External Services
    RayHead -->|pull images| Registry[Container Registry<br/>Required]
    RayHead -->|fetch code/data| Storage[Git / S3 / GCS<br/>Required]
    RayHead -->|runtime deps| PyPI[Ray Package Index<br/>Required]

    %% Integration Points
    DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|submit jobs| KubeRay
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -.->|Ray client| RayHead

    %% Monitoring Integration
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| KubeRay
    Prometheus -->|scrapes| RayHead

